"Peace through power." - Kane, leader of the Brotherhood of Nod.

@chingma8064 the full quote from the game "Command & Conquer: Tiberium Sun" goes like this:

"Rise, my people. I have returned, never to leave your side again. GDI sought to destroy me, but they have only made me stronger. Today, we march forward into our future. A stronger people, a divined people, enhanced for the Tiberium world. The time has come to claim this world as our own! The time has come to destroy GDI! One vision, one purpose! Peace through power!"

Now a lot of that quote is derived from Kane talking about the Technology of Peace which was NOD's Tiberium technology. Kane was seeking to accelerate human evolution through the use of an in-world substance called Tiberium, which was an alien mineral brought to Earth via a meteorite impact near the Tiber River in Italy, thus its name. Kane sought to destroy the global military superpower, the Global Defense Initiative (GDI), in order to spread Tiberium across the world.

